   122	
   123	## Stage 2 Frame and Schema Check
   124	
   125	Task 026 adds a deterministic regression for the stage-2 frame boundary and
   126	2-DOF arm schema. It does not start PX4, Gazebo, Micro XRCE-DDS, or any ROS
   127	nodes.
   128	
   129	Run from the workspace root:
   130	
   131	```bash
   132	python3 scripts/check_stage2_schema.py
   133	```
   134	
   135	Passing output contains:
   136	
   137	```text
   138	CHECK=PASS report=logs/demo_06_state_agg/<timestamp>/tf_report.json
   139	```
   140	
   141	The generated `tf_report.json` uses
   142	`stage2_frame_schema_regression_v1` and records every enforced invariant. The
   143	checker currently enforces:
   144	
   145	- frame names: `map`, `uav/base_link`, `uav/arm_base`, `uav/ee_link`,
   146	  `uav/camera_link`;
   147	- TF chain: `map -> uav/base_link -> uav/arm_base -> uav/ee_link ->
   148	  uav/camera_link`;
   149	- NED-to-ENU TF conversion: `enu_x=ned_y`, `enu_y=ned_x`, `enu_z=-ned_z`;
   150	- NED/ENU round trips for `(0, 0, 0)`, `(1, 2, -3)`, and
   151	  `(-4.5, 0.25, 2.0)`;
   152	- 2-DOF arm joint names: `arm_shoulder_pitch_joint`,
   153	  `arm_elbow_pitch_joint`;
   154	- two-element arm vectors for positions, velocities, efforts, limits, and
   155	  default velocity limits;
   156	- `ArmCommand`, `ArmState`, `PlatformState`, and `SystemObservation` message
   157	  fields that make up the stage-2 state schema.
   158	
   159	Use a fixed timestamp when a reproducible report path is needed:
   160	
   161	```bash
   162	python3 scripts/check_stage2_schema.py --timestamp 20260527_026_regression
   163	```
   164	
   165	## Demo 10 Air Reach Check
   166	
   167	Demo 10 combines the stage-2 UAV bridge, tag target pose, approach coordinator,
   168	arm bridge, and episode recorder into an air-reach regression. The default
   169	runner is safe for development machines that do not currently have PX4/Gazebo
   170	running:

